  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Demonstrate the acute effects of ketamine on endogenous µ-opioid neurotransmission in humans.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study will test the hypothesis that the rapidly-acting antidepressant ketamine improves
      core depressive symptoms by acutely activating the brain's endogenous µ-opioid system.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
